One shareholder file suit, e dey find out sey di Unitel Video Inc wan buy di new joinbody wey dey closely hold Kenmare Capital Corp, for $15 a share, or $33.6 million.

Di suit wey dey find class action, dem come file am for Delaware Chancery Court.

Di complain be sey di price na yeye, yeye o, and sey defendants dey find on top di buy of Unitel, thereby discouraging oda bids.

E dey find big money wey no go last.

New York company dey call di lawsuit witout merit.

Shareholder suppose vote on top di transaction Nov.

